SUMMARY:Webinar: The GutBrain Connection: Mindfulness\, Stress the Power o
 f Awareness
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever had a gut feeling you couldnt explain? Stress do
 esnt just live in your headit shows up in your gut. Your gut and brain are
  in constant conversation\, shaping mood\, digestion\, and overall well-be
 ing. In this engaging talk\, well explore the gutbrain connection and how 
 mindfulness\, awareness\, and everyday habits influence both stress and he
 alth. Youll walk away with simple\, practical tools to calm your nervous s
 ystem\, listen to your bodys signals\, and build lasting gutmind resilienc
 e. Presented by Bay Care and UHC Onsite Nurse Liaison. This webinar does c
 ount toward your wellness incentive benefit - 100  quarter. Registration: 
 4.1.26 Gut Brain Connection (https:events.teams.microsoft.comeventfed3bfd2
 -76ca-4b27-aaf9-a3ed26603dc4db05faca-c82a-4b9d-b9c5-0f64b6755421) \n\nPerm
 alink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/185281
