SUMMARY:BayCare Presents - Mental Health vs. Mental Illness: Whats the Dif
 ference?
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Mental health and mental illness are often used interchangeabl
 ybut theyre not the same. This presentation breaks down the differences\, 
 helping participants understand how mental wellness can exist even with a 
 diagnosis\, and how mental illness can impact daily life. Join us to explo
 re common misconceptions\, learn supportive language\, and discover ways t
 o promote mental well-being in our community. Click here to join the meeti
 ng (https:teams.microsoft.commeet25108891955457?p2Eq3JmmfO3nETNnJjA) \n\nP
 ermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/178701
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/178701
END:VEVENT
