DTEND:20260514T164500Z
SUMMARY:BayCare Presents: Im Fine\, Its Fine\, Everythings Fine!
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Saying Im fine can be short and sweet but doesnt usually give 
 an accurate description of our emotions. Sometimes we use\, Im fine to mas
 k feelings\, avoid conflict\, and pretend that everything is okay. This pr
 esentation will explore what it means to minimize\, ways we can acknowledg
 e and honor how we feel in the present moment and how we can take ownershi
 p of our emotions in the new year to navigate us to our authentic selves. 
 May 14\, 2026 Lisa Moser\, Psy.D 12-12:45 pm Register Here (https:events.t
 eams.microsoft.comevent88276a51-66e1-4ffe-ba0e-339dad737ce5599ceff3-02a8-4
 5bc-baef-c48cb8be94c4) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/178246
